attributes.review: I opened the app for the first time, and it immediately crashed. Then I tried again, and it crashed. Finally, on my 3rd try I was able to get in but then the second I got it on it froze and I had to close the app. On my fourth time opening the app, it did not crash or freeze and I was finally able to see the graphics. However they were absolutely terrible and they looked like they were designed by a child. The app also detected my location and it told me that it was sending me a representative to finish setting it up. However, the person they sent was my annoying teacher from school and I slammed the door on her. Over all a terrible experience and I would not recommend to anyone.
attributes.title: Complete Disappointment

attributes.review: Did you ever hear the Tragedy of Darth Plagueis the Wise? No. I thought not. It’s not a story the Jedi would tell you. It's a Sith legend. Darth Plagueis was a Dark Lord of the Sith, so powerful and so wise he could use the Force to influence the midichlorians to create life... He had such a knowledge of the dark side that he could even keep the ones he cared about from dying. He could actually save save people from death? The dark side of the Force is a pathway to many abilities some consider to be unnatural. What happened to him? He became so powerful... the only thing he was afraid of was losing his power, which eventually, of course, he did. Unfortunately, he taught his apprentice everything he knew, then his apprentice killed him in his sleep. It's ironic he could save others from death, but not himself.
